chart: sequence
title: 29.1 Async / Fire-and-Forget Messages

User -> API: POST /order
API -> OrderDB: saveOrder(data) <- orderId
API ~> EmailSvc: Send confirmation
API ~> AuditLog: Log order created
API -> PaymentSvc: charge(orderId) <- 200 OK
PaymentSvc -> NotifySvc: Payment processed
PaymentSvc -> API: chargeResult
